short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Finds links to Figma files and shows an embedded version of them next to the link.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension runs on github.com by default. Click the extension button to run it on other domains.

Click while holding Command/Ctrl to expand or collapse all links.
